islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"82a69bce7300d8afcf4c9da3cb654bbf114cd0db","tid":1790593,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"28e2d5b26b53017520b6f5d8fb40798881f4dc93","tid":1790593,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d811edbfed7276d425862d04a01067308eda57","tid":1790593,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"大家星期六有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5SVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=2a40d91f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"bcdf5e324235f4fb30dc8aa9cb65d3ae2c4cace3","tid":1790593,"uid":259732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c20aca898089bce75ed862130948e80c5d2ffbd","tid":1790593,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係台灣發大財"},{"pid":"32fa89536d365e37f82b090d267382e268923f54","tid":1790593,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"其實，與其俾美商支那續命<br />\n不如俾佢地叫台灣開廠"},{"pid":"fd76365813481d36a666f8aa7ddf129f541b370d","tid":1790593,"uid"